FOR MENn 4 drops jasmine, 7 drops patchouli, 4 drops black pepper
10 drops cedarwood, 5 drops rosemary, 5 drops orange
3 drops oakmoss, 10 drops sandalwood, 2 drops rose otto
FOR WOMENn 10ml infused vanilla oil as a base, 8 drops ylang ylang, 4 drops
rose absolut, 3 drops lime
4 drops jasmine, 5 drops clary sage, 8 drops bergamot
4 drops carnation, 6 drops coriander, 6 drops bergamot
